      "text": "さっき観た映画、思わず泣いちゃったよ\n王道のラブストーリーだったけど、楽しめた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The movie we just saw‚ I ended up crying!\nIt was a typical love story‚ did you enjoy it?",
