      "text": "うん、面白かったよ！\n主人公と仲良しなシーンが沢山あって良かった～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was fun!\nI liked that there're lots of scenes where the main characters were close to each other~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0826075237,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
