      "text": "ふふ。私、ずーっと胸がキュンキュンしてたよ\n特に一番ドキドキしたのは、あのシーンなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. My heart was fluttering the whole time\nEspecially‚ that scene was the most exciting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3093650182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
